    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=xumlrtoq93]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xumlrtoq93]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=j885e0lqxh]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=j885e0lqxh]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=yyfizni11h]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=yyfizni11h]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=o8jod0d73w]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=o8jod0d73w]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=a27krgkyig]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=a27krgkyig]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"ExternalLearning-ExternalLearningResources\"><span data-colorid=\"o8jod0d73w\">External Learning Resources</span></h1><p>Our RenderMan community is unlike any other, and here you&rsquo;ll find some practical external learning and training resources for you to get stuck into!</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://graphics.pixar.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"graphicspixar.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/graphicspixar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758186751482&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/506298373/graphicspixar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758186751482&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606306328\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"graphicspixar.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"506298373\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"9cf6815f-47c4-479c-9b03-c3b17b795b5e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/graphicspixar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758186751482&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/graphicspixar.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758186751482&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"ExternalLearning-PixarGraphics\"><span data-colorid=\"yyfizni11h\">Pixar Graphics </span></h1><p>Pixar Research has a long history of technological innovation and pioneering work in computer graphics and animated films.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.fxphd.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"fxphd-docs-thumb.webp\" width=\"583\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/fxphd-docs-thumb.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759335389803&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=583&amp;height=253\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/506298373/fxphd-docs-thumb.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759335389803&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"617447525\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"fxphd-docs-thumb.webp\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/webp\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"506298373\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"b3259a6a-0b15-4fe6-ab71-22d2d2a56bf8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/fxphd-docs-thumb.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759335389803&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/fxphd-docs-thumb.webp?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759335389803&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=583&amp;height=253 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"ExternalLearning-fxphd\"><span data-colorid=\"xumlrtoq93\">fxphd</span></h1><p>Our friends at fxphd offer a fantastic set of RenderMan courses, designed by and for professionals.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@TheNotepadShow/featured\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"notepadshow.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/notepadshow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187132087&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/506298373/notepadshow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187132087&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606142491\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"notepadshow.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"506298373\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"baad95ba-18d0-4ee6-9998-52b7c9450736\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/notepadshow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187132087&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/notepadshow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187132087&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"ExternalLearning-TheNotePadShow\"><span data-colorid=\"a27krgkyig\">The NotePad Show</span></h1><p>The Notepad Show is your go to place for learning all the ins and outs of RenderMan and its integrations into your favorite DCCs.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@MeshmenStudio/featured\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"meshmen studio.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/meshmen%20studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187442823&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/506298373/meshmen%20studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187442823&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606306335\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"meshmen studio.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"506298373\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"c2608da8-68d9-4d57-bfc9-ae770636fb7e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/meshmen%20studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187442823&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/meshmen%20studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758187442823&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"ExternalLearning-MeshMenStudio\"><span data-colorid=\"j885e0lqxh\">MeshMen Studio</span></h1><p>VFX, Texturing, and Look Development Tutorials and Projects by Peter Aversten, whose motto is to help artists one Pixel at a time.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762606591989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/506298373/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762606591989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621505\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"506298373\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"23\" data-media-id=\"d694908d-5037-481a-b1ba-4827bbf458a5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762606591989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/506298373/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762606591989&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
